                <ul>
                    <li>Negotiate a raise or promotion — even a small increase can shift your DTI several percentage points</li>
                    <li>Add a co-borrower (spouse, partner) to combine incomes on the mortgage application</li>
                    <li>Start a side hustle or freelance work — lenders typically want 2 years of documented income</li>
                    <li>Include bonuses, overtime, rental income, or investment income if consistent and documented</li>
